OL,3,CWhat are my rights if my workplace is
OL,4,Ctoo hot?
OL,6,FThe heat has continued into the
OL,7,Fworking week, with temperatures still
OL,8,Fexpected to reach 35C in some parts of
OL,9,Fthe country on Tuesday, leaving
OL,10,Fworkers, from builders to office
OL,11,Fstaff, sweltering outside or inside
OL,12,Fwith little or no access to air
OL,13,Fconditioning.
OL,15,FSo what are your rights if it's too
OL,16,Fhot to work? ITV News explains.
OL,18,FWhat if it's too hot to work?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
