OL,7,Femployers on managing excessive heat,
OL,8,Fwhich workers may also find useful
OL,9,Fwhen discussing ways to improve
OL,10,Fconditions in the workplace.
OL,12,FThe HSE recommends employers:
OL,14,FEmployers can also adapt working
OL,15,Fpatterns by:
